===Etymology===
[[w:Greek language|Greek]][[Category:Greek derivations]] ''tri'', "[[three]]" + ''lēmma'', "auxiliary proposition"

===Noun===
'''trilemma''' (''plural:'' '''trilemmata''' ''or'' '''trilemmas''')
{{wikipedia}}
